## compounding frequency
## effective interst rate
## 10% interst rate compounded monthly
## ear=((1+r/m)**m)-1
ear=((1+.10/12)**12)-1
((1+.12/12)**12)-1
0.126825/12
## how compunding effect annual paymemts of annuity
